<plot>A man wakes into shot. But how awake is he as he meanders through his morning routine in a house that isn't quite right? His wake-up call arrives in the shape of an increasingly exasperated Samaritan, driven to extreme means of encouragement. An ambiguous tale of self-induced pity, serving as a warning to those settling into a life half-asleep.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052869</url></doc>
